text: I appeared on this show with @Larry_kudlow on many occasions!
"Cuddles" is one of the nicest people I have ever met! From my perch he can do no wrong! @larry_kudlow

Dear Mom, Happy Mothers Day... There's a story behind everything. How a picture got on a wall. How a scar got on my face. Sometimes the stories are simple, and sometimes they are hard and heartbreaking.
But behind all my stories is always your story, because yours is where mine begin.
